title: THE MANDALORIAN Episode 2 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed! "The Child"
author: Think Story
comment: this is how Star Wars movies should be made. Absolutely awesome !!!!
“Pay child support, I will not! Go to Dagobah, I must, act homeless and mentally ill, I will.” - Yoda
Getting to see the Jawa's operate and defend their fortress was something I've wondered about and wanted to see since I was a child.

Why does everyone talking about the Mandalorian's knife, not realize that it's a vibro-blade? You can literally see it vibrating when he holds it up to defend himself. The reason it killed the mud-horn is because of it's ability to cut deep beyond the physical blade itself, due to the vibrations. If that were a normal knife he would have failed to kill the beast.
